<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,274,1856,1881]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">FIGURE 6.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Hancock 1909" authorityName="Hancock" authorityYear="1909" box="[280,566,1856,1881]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Scaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brevis">
<emphasis box="[280,413,1857,1881]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Scaria brevis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Hancock, J. L." box="[419,566,1856,1881]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="387 - 426" refId="ref31709" refString="Hancock, J. L. (1909 [1908]) Further studies of the Tetriginae (Orthoptera) in the Oxford University Museum. Transactions of the Entomological Society of London, 56 (3 - 4), 387 - 426. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 2311.1909. tb 02160. x" type="journal article" year="1909">Hancock 1909</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
type (= 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Cadena-Castañeda &amp; Mendes &amp; Silva &amp; Granda &amp; García &amp; Tumbrinck" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="Hancock" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[644,836,1857,1881]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Batrachidea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brevis" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[644,836,1857,1881]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Batrachidea brevis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[841,956,1857,1881]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[841,956,1857,1881]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[971,996,1856,1881]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">A.</emphasis>
Habitus in lateral view and labels. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1350,1373,1857,1881]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">B.</emphasis>
Habitus in dorsal view. (Photos: Hope Entomological Collections).
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,1963,2025]" lastBlockId="17.[151,1436,153,251]" lastPageId="17" lastPageNumber="18" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
With this panorama expounded so far, it is suggested that 
<taxonomicName authority="Hebard, 1923" authorityName="Hebard" authorityYear="1923" baseAuthorityName="Hebard" baseAuthorityYear="1923" box="[858,1269,1963,1989]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Batrachidea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inermis" status="syn. nov.">
<emphasis box="[858,1089,1963,1989]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Batrachidea inermis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hebard, M." box="[1104,1261,1963,1989]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="165 - 313" refId="ref31865" refString="Hebard, M. (1923) Studies in the Dermaptera and Orthoptera of Colombia. Third paper. Orthopterous family Acrididae. Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 49, 165 - 313." type="journal article" year="1923">Hebard, 1923</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1277,1382,1963,1989]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1277,1382,1963,1989]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">syn. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, is a synonym and conspecific female for 
<taxonomicName authority="(Hancock, 1909)" authorityName="Cadena-Castañeda &amp; Mendes &amp; Silva &amp; Granda &amp; García &amp; Tumbrinck" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="Hancock" baseAuthorityYear="1909" box="[569,980,1999,2025]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Batrachidea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brevis" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[569,783,1999,2025]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Batrachidea brevis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hancock, J. L." box="[798,971,1999,2025]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="387 - 426" refId="ref31709" refString="Hancock, J. L. (1909 [1908]) Further studies of the Tetriginae (Orthoptera) in the Oxford University Museum. Transactions of the Entomological Society of London, 56 (3 - 4), 387 - 426. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 2311.1909. tb 02160. x" type="journal article" year="1909">Hancock, 1909</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[988,1117,1999,2025]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[988,1117,1999,2025]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, and these latter fits charac- ters of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Serville" authorityYear="1838" box="[233,371,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Batrachidea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[233,371,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Batrachidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
better, not those of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bolivar" authorityYear="1887" box="[604,677,153,179]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Scaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[604,677,153,179]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Scaria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. These nomenclatural acts are performed upon reviewing the 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,153,179]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">type</typeStatus>
specimens and additional ones collected, observed and photographed in the field (
<bibRefCitation author="Cardona, J. M." box="[1087,1258,189,215]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" refId="ref30870" refString="Cardona, J. M. (2012) Grasshoppers of Northwest South America. A Photo Guide. Vol. 1. The Western Fauna. Blurb. com, Medellin, 124 pp." type="book" year="2012">Cardona, 2012</bibRefCitation>
, pags. 114, 115 determined as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bolivar" authorityYear="1887" box="[314,387,225,251]" class="Insecta" family="Tetrigidae" genus="Scaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[314,387,225,251]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Scaria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp.) and the collection of Filippo Maria Buzzetti as quoted by 
<bibRefCitation author="Buzzetti, F. M. &amp; Devriese, H." box="[1090,1403,225,251]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" pagination="41 - 54" refId="ref30532" refString="Buzzetti, F. M. &amp; Devriese, H. (2007) Tetrigidae from Ecuador (Orthoptera Caelifera Tetrigoidea). Atti della Accademia Roveretana degli Agiati, Series 8, VII (B), 41 - 54." type="book chapter" year="2007">Buzzetti &amp; Devriese (2007)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
